net.sf.mmm.client.ui.api.feature

Interface UiFeatureOpenClose

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AttributeReadVisible, AttributeWriteVisible, UiFeature
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    UiWidgetAbstractDialogWindow, UiWidgetPopup, UiWidgetWindow
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractUiWidgetAbstractDialogWindow, AbstractUiWidgetPopup, AbstractUiWidgetWindow, UiWidgetCustomAbstractDialogWindow, UiWidgetCustomPopup, UiWidgetPopupGwt, UiWidgetPopupTestImpl, UiWidgetWindowGwt

    public interface UiFeatureOpenClose
extends UiFeature, AttributeWriteVisible
    This is the interface for the features of an object (e.g. a window) that can be opened and closed. It allows to add and remove instances of close handlers as well as open handlers.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Joerg Hohwiller (hohwille at users.sourceforge.net)
